        <h2 style="font-size: 40px;">Contact Information and Locations:</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 40px;">
            The university's website provides detailed information on the various emergency services available on campus, below are the respective contact detail of the most important emergency contacts in case a pesron finds an urge or need to contact them</p>
            <br>
            <br>
            <br><br><br>
